│ unwind destination for an\n  // invoke.  The logic for finding the matching cleanupret would be too\n  // complex.  This is  │
│ a rare case, so we'll just miss the optimization.\n  for (BasicBlock *Pred : predecessors(PadBB)) {\n    TerminatorInst      │
│ *Term = Pred->getTerminator();\n    if (isa<InvokeInst>(Term))\n      return false;\n  }\n"                                  │
